Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.26,Text-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\fs60\fsp0\frz9.38\fax0.1\1c&H28342A&\move(1464.6,715.1,1189.47,420.44,25,2945)}真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.26,Text-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\fs60\fsp0\frz9.38\fax0.1\1c&H242725&\move(886.83,841.96,611.7,547.3,25,2945)}没事，我也才刚到。\N我就在西出口的外面。
